mediaDetails.ext_alt_text:
confetti_ball New club looking for members tada

KCD Learning Club

Club Curriculum: https://epicreact.dev/

Club Captain: @Saphal 🚀

Learning Goal Summary: To learn React the epic way!

Requirements:
      - Basic Javascript
      - Willingness to learn

Club Schedule:
      Wednesday at 18:00 +5:30 (IST)
      - Week 0 (before the first meeting): Welcome to Epic React (watch the intro and setup videos)
      - Week 1: React Fundamentals
      - Week 2: React Hooks
      - Week 3: Build an Epic React App Part 1:
        - Render a React App
        - Add Styles
        - Make HTTP Requests
      - Week 4: Advanced React Hooks
      - Week 5: Build an Epic React App Part 2:
        - Authentication
        - Routing
      - Week 6: Advanced React Patterns
      - Week 7: Build an Epic React App Part 3:
        - Cache Management
      - Week 8: Build an Epic React App Part 4:
        - Context
        - Compound Components
      - Week 9: React Performance
      - Week 10: Build an Ep
